类 GatherSumApplyIteration<K,VV,EV,M>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.graph.gsa.GatherSumApplyIteration<K,VV,EV,M>
  • 类型参数:
    K - The type of the vertex key in the graph
    VV - The type of the vertex value in the graph
    EV - The type of the edge value in the graph
    M - The intermediate type used by the gather, sum and apply functions

extends java.lang.Object
implements CustomUnaryOperation<Vertex<K,VV>,Vertex<K,VV>>
    This class represents iterative graph computations, programmed in a gather-sum-apply perspective.

      • withEdges

        public static <K,VV,EV,M> GatherSumApplyIteration<K,VV,EV,M> withEdges(DataSet<Edge<K,EV>> edges,

                                                                       SumFunction<VV,EV,M> sum,
                                                                       ApplyFunction<K,VV,M> apply,
                                                                       int maximumNumberOfIterations)
        Creates a new gather-sum-apply iteration operator for graphs.
        类型参数:
        K - The type of the vertex key in the graph
        VV - The type of the vertex value in the graph
        EV - The type of the edge value in the graph
        M - The intermediate type used by the gather, sum and apply functions
        参数:
        edges - The edge DataSet
        gather - The gather function of the GSA iteration
        sum - The sum function of the GSA iteration
        apply - The apply function of the GSA iteration
        maximumNumberOfIterations - The maximum number of iterations executed
        返回:
        An in stance of the gather-sum-apply graph computation operator.
